h1 Create Users
p POST /api/users.json?api_key=secret

strong Body
pre
  code
    | { name: 'Hi', phone: '+13211231234' }

strong Response
pre
  code
    | { user: { id: 123, name: 'Hi', phone: '+13211231234', token: 'jfioadspjfiaspdfjdsifp' } }

