h1 Add Buddies
p POST /api/buddies.json?api_key=secret&token=[user_token]

strong Body
pre
  code
    | { buddies: [{ name: 'Hi', phone: '+11231231234' }, { name: 'Bro', phone: '+11231231235' }] }

